a.n: The Amazing World of Gumball I

p.k: The Pressure / The Painting / The Responsible / The Dress Gumball tries to save Darwin from being kissed by a girl. / Principal Brown tries to “fix” Gumball’s dysfunctional family. / Gumball and Darwin babysit Anais “responsibly” whilst “irresponsibly” flooding the house. / Gumball goes to school in a dress and becomes the darling of Elmore High.
